free state south of johannesburg police said the report did not 
specify when the incidents took place 
zonkezizwe was the scene of a weekend massacre in which 19 black 
men were hacked and stabbed to death police said they have not 
determined a motive for the slayings but residents said the 
township had been the scene of fighting between members of the 
xhosa and zulu tribes 
zulus comprise the bulk of support for the inkatha freedom party 
