been calling around the world to the families of everyone he has 
photographed and every gallery that displays his work telling 
them he is a pornographer and child molester and hunting for any 
possible evidence against him 
its evidence of a government thats run amok sturges said 
at a news conference 
it does not take seven months to study a handful of pictures 
unless of course you become obsessed with them added attorney 
michael metzger 
the case started when a photo lab employee told the fbi that a 
