income through increased sales of prints 
asked when the case might be resolved us attorney william 
mcgivern said we cant pin ourselves to deadlines either 
imposed by potential defendants or imposed by the press 
he said senior prosecutors in his office were still 
reviewing the case and had not yet decided whether to ask him to 
seek a grand jury indictment 
