president bushs persian gulf policy is being 
tested on the home front in senate hearings this week and next 
forums for debate and defense of the course that threatens war with 
iraq 
force at least the threat of it is an option bush wants 
strengthened not put into question to that end he needs solid 
not slipping support in congress and the country 
