government proposal for a 30 percent capital gains tax they fear 
that the way the government intends to collect the tax will scare 
investors away from the stock market and shift business to other 
european markets 
the government has said it is willing to consider technical 
improvements in the implementation of the law but that it isnt 
willing to renounce the capital gains tax itself 
